<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>兩院區藥品互領系統</title>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:"Noto Sans TC",Arial,sans-serif;background:#F4F5F7;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:14px;}
.hidden{display:none!important;}
#app-header{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:0 20px;height:48px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.header-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;}
.logo-icon{width:28px;height:28px;background:#185FA5;border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
nav{display:flex;gap:2px;}
.nav-btn{padding:5px 12px;border-radius:6px;border:none;background:transparent;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;color:#6b7280;font-family:inherit;}
.nav-btn.active{background:#EFF6FF;color:#185FA5;font-weight:600;}
.nav-btn:hover:not(.active){background:#f3f4f6;}
.header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;}
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;}
.badge-dl{background:#DBEAFE;color:#1e40af;}
.badge-hw{background:#D1FAE5;color:#065f46;}
.badge-gen{background:#F3F4F6;color:#374151;}
.badge-c12{background:#FEE2E2;color:#991b1b;}
.badge-c3{background:#FEF3C7;color:#92400e;}
.badge-emg{background:#FEE2E2;color:#991b1b;border:1px solid #fca5a5;}
.badge-pend{background:#FEF3C7;color:#92400e;border:1px solid #fcd34d;}
#main-content{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.btn{padding:7px 16px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #d1d5db;background:#fff;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all 0.15s;}
.btn:hover{background:#f9fafb;}
.btn:active{transform:scale(0.98);}
.btn-primary{background:#185FA5;border-color:#185FA5;color:#fff;}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#1e429f;}
.btn-primary:disabled{background:#93c5fd;border-color:#93c5fd;cursor:not-allowed;}
.form-group{margin-bottom:14px;}
.form-label{display:block;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:4px;font-weight:500;}
.form-input{width:100%;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #d1d5db;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;background:#fff;}
.form-input:focus{border-color:#185FA5;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px #DBEAFE;}
select.form-input{cursor:pointer;}
#login-screen{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;}
.stats-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.stat-card{background:#F9FAFB;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;}
.stat-label{font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:4px;}
.stat-value{font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:#111;}
.table-wrap{overflow-x:auto;}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;min-width:600px;}
th{text-align:left;padding:8px 10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;background:#F9FAFB;white-space:nowrap;}
td{padding:8px 10px;font-size:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;}
tr:hover td{background:#fafafa;}
.mono{font-family:monospace;font-size:11px;}
.campus-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 24px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:16px;}
.campus-box{text-align:center;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 6px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;background:#F9FAFB;}
.campus-box.emergency{background:#FEF2F2;border-color:#fca5a5;}
.campus-box-label{font-size:10px;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:5px;}
.campus-box-label.emg{color:#dc2626;font-weight:600;}
.campus-box select{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;background:transparent;border:none;outline:none;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;width:100%;color:#111;font-family:inherit;}
.drug-info{background:#EFF6FF;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.drug-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:5px;font-size:12px;}
.drug-row:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
.drug-row-label{color:#1e40af;}
.drug-row-value{font-weight:600;color:#1e3a8a;font-family:monospace;font-size:11px;}
.drug-row-value.nm{font-family:inherit;font-size:12px;}
.success-toast{background:#ECFDF5;border:1px solid #6ee7b7;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.alert{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start;}
.alert-warning{background:#FEF3C7;border:1px solid #fcd34d;color:#78350f;}
.alert-danger{background:#FEF2F2;border:1px solid #fca5a5;color:#7f1d1d;}
.alert-info{background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;color:#1e3a8a;}
.user-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-size:12px;}
.admin-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#374151;margin-bottom:8px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="login-screen">
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:340px;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
      <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
        <div class="logo-icon">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#111;">藥品互領系統</span>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:4px;">斗六院區 ／ 虎尾院區</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="padding:24px;">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">員工編號</label>
        <input class="form-input" id="login-emp" placeholder="請輸入員編" autocomplete="username"/>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">密碼 <span style="font-weight:400;color:#9ca3af;">（預設與員編相同）</span></label>
        <input type="password" class="form-input" id="login-pwd" placeholder="請輸入密碼" autocomplete="current-password"/>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label class="form-label">所屬院區</label>
        <select class="form-input" id="login-campus">
          <option value="douliou">斗六院區</option>
          <option value="huwei">虎尾院區</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div id="login-error" class="hidden" style="color:#dc2626;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:10px;background:#FEF2F2;padding:8px 10px;border-radius:6px;"></div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;padding:10px;" id="login-btn">登入</button>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;margin-top:12px;">如需重設密碼，請聯絡系統管理員</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="app-screen" class="hidden">
  <div id="app-header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
        <div class="logo-icon">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#111;">藥品互領系統</span>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <button class="nav-btn active" id="nav-scan">掃碼收藥</button>
        <button class="nav-btn" id="nav-records">互領紀錄</button>
        <button class="nav-btn" id="nav-reports">報表</button>
        <button class="nav-btn" id="nav-admin">管理</button>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="header-right">
      <span id="header-user"></span>
      <button class="btn" style="font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;" id="logout-btn">登出</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="main-content">
    <div id="tab-scan">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">今日互領筆數</div><div class="stat-value" id="cnt-today">－</div></div>
        <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">本週累計</div><div class="stat-value" id="cnt-week">－</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" id="scan-idle-card">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <div style="width:44px;height:44px;background:#EFF6FF;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#185FA5" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 5v14M7 5v14M11 5v14M15 5v10M19 5v14M15 17v2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#111;">等待刷條碼</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:2px;">用條碼機刷藥袋條碼，系統自動帶入資料</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position:relative;">
          <input class="form-input" id="barcode-input" placeholder="請刷條碼，或手動輸入後按 Enter" style="font-family:monospace;font-size:12px;padding-right:70px;" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"/>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="barcode-submit-btn" style="position:absolute;right:4px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);padding:4px 10px;font-size:11px;">確認</button>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;">條碼機刷入後自動送出，無需按任何按鍵</div>
        <div id="barcode-processing" class="hidden" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;color:#185FA5;">查詢藥品中...</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card hidden" id="scan-confirm-card">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:14px;">
          <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;">確認收藥資訊</div>
          <span class="badge" id="confirm-badge">待確認</span>
        </div>
        <div id="emergency-alert" class="alert alert-danger hidden">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          <div><strong>急診處方（E字頭）</strong>，兩院區共用，請手動確認開方院區及領藥院區。</div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;margin-bottom:12px;">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;"><span style="color:#6b7280;">病患帳號</span><span class="mono" id="ci-account"></span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;"><span style="color:#6b7280;">病歷號</span><span class="mono" id="ci-pid"></span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:5px 0;"><span style="color:#6b7280;">領藥號</span><span class="mono" id="ci-dispno"></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="drug-info">
          <div class="drug-row"><span class="drug-row-label">藥品台大碼</span><span class="drug-row-value" id="ci-drugcode"></span></div>
          <div class="drug-row"><span class="drug-row-label">庫存碼</span><span class="drug-row-value" id="ci-stockcode"></span></div>
          <div class="drug-row"><span class="drug-row-label">商品名</span><span class="drug-row-value nm" id="ci-name"></span></div>
          <div class="drug-row"><span class="drug-row-label">數量 / 單位</span><span class="drug-row-value nm" id="ci-qty"></span></div>
          <div class="drug-row"><span class="drug-row-label">管制類別</span><span id="ci-ctrl"></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="campus-grid">
          <div class="campus-box" id="prescribe-box">
            <div class="campus-box-label" id="prescribe-label">開方院區（自動）</div>
            <select id="prescribe-sel"><option value="douliou">斗六院區</option><option value="huwei">虎尾院區</option></select>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9ca3af" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="campus-box" id="dispense-box">
            <div class="campus-box-label" id="dispense-label">領藥院區（自動）</div>
            <div id="dispense-fixed" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#065f46;"></div>
            <select id="dispense-sel" class="hidden"><option value="douliou">斗六院區</option><option value="huwei">虎尾院區</option></select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" style="flex:1;padding:9px;" id="confirm-btn">確認</button>
          <button class="btn" style="flex:1;padding:9px;" id="cancel-btn">取消</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="success-toast hidden" id="scan-success-toast">
        <div style="width:32px;height:32px;background:#A7F3D0;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#065f46" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#065f46;">收藥完成，可刷下一筆</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:#059669;margin-top:1px;" id="success-drug-info"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card hidden" id="scan-error-card" style="text-align:center;padding:24px;">
        <div style="width:44px;height:44px;background:#FEF2F2;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 10px;">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#991b1b;margin-bottom:4px;">發生錯誤</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:14px;" id="error-msg"></div>
        <button class="btn" id="retry-btn">重新刷碼</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-records" class="hidden">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;">
        <input type="date" class="form-input" id="rec-date" style="width:auto;"/>
        <select class="form-input" id="rec-type" style="width:auto;">
          <option value="all">全部藥品</option><option value="general">一般藥品</option>
          <option value="ctrl12">管一二級</option><option value="ctrl3">管三級</option>
        </select>
        <button class="btn" id="rec-search-btn" style="font-size:12px;">查詢</button>
        <span style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;margin-left:auto;" id="rec-count"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:0;">
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr>
              <th>時間</th><th>病歷號</th><th>領藥號</th><th>藥品台大碼</th><th>庫存碼</th>
              <th>商品名</th><th>數量</th><th>單位</th><th>類別</th><th>開方</th><th>領藥</th>
            </tr></thead>
            <tbody id="records-tbody"><tr><td colspan="11" style="text-align:center;padding:20px;color:#9ca3af;">請選擇日期後查詢</td></tr></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-reports" class="hidden">
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-end;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div>
          <div class="form-label">報表日期</div>
          <input type="date" class="form-input" id="rpt-date" style="width:auto;"/>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:8px;">選好日期後點各報表的「匯出 Excel」</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:10px;">
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;">一般藥品互領報表</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:2px;">含藥品明細及淨額統計</div></div>
            <span class="badge badge-dl">明細＋淨額</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
            <select class="form-input" id="rpt-general-type" style="width:auto;font-size:12px;"><option value="daily">日報表</option><option value="weekly">週報表</option></select>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:12px;" id="export-general-btn">匯出 Excel</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:10px;">
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;">管一二級藥品報表（日報表）</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:2px;">逐筆明細，含核對欄位</div></div>
            <span class="badge badge-c12">逐筆明細</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" style="font-size:12px;border-color:#fca5a5;color:#991b1b;" id="export-ctrl12-btn">匯出 Excel</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:10px;">
            <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;">管三級藥品報表（日報表）</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:2px;">逐筆明細，含核對欄位</div></div>
            <span class="badge badge-c3">逐筆明細</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn" style="font-size:12px;border-color:#fcd34d;color:#92400e;" id="export-ctrl3-btn">匯出 Excel</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-warning" style="margin-top:12px;">管制藥品報表需逐筆核對後，依藥庫庫存碼辦理轉帳。</div>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-admin" class="hidden">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="admin-title">藥師帳號管理</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <input class="form-input" id="new-emp" placeholder="員編" style="width:100px;"/>
          <input class="form-input" id="new-name" placeholder="姓名" style="width:100px;"/>
          <select class="form-input" id="new-campus" style="width:auto;"><option value="douliou">斗六</option><option value="huwei">虎尾</option></select>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:12px;" id="add-user-btn">新增藥師</button>
        </div>
        <div id="user-list"></div>
        <div style="margin-top:20px;" class="admin-title">藥品主檔更新</div>
        <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-bottom:10px;">上傳新的藥品主檔 Excel，系統會自動更新（格式需與原本相同）</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <input type="file" id="drug-file" accept=".xlsx,.xls" style="font-size:12px;"/>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:12px;" id="import-btn">匯入更新</button>
        </div>
        <div id="import-status" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
(function() {
  // ── Config ──────────────────────────────────────────────
  var SUPA_URL = "https://aczjtsxwovuxjukaieys.supabase.co";
